		<title>臺東東海岸香草魅力綻放 從產地培力到行銷市集打造永續農村</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/26/%e8%87%ba%e6%9d%b1%e6%9d%b1%e6%b5%b7%e5%b2%b8%e9%a6%99%e8%8d%89%e9%ad%85%e5%8a%9b%e7%b6%bb%e6%94%be-%e5%be%9e%e7%94%a2%e5%9c%b0%e5%9f%b9%e5%8a%9b%e5%88%b0%e8%a1%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%b8%82%e9%9b%86%e6%89%93/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報]]></dc:creator>
